    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on that? Maybe have him describe what he actually sees when he looks at the tribespeople—like their temperament or how they carry themselves compared to Europeans. He should explain why he thinks they're incapable of governing themselves without this outside help.",
