      "content": "That's intense and really hits that period tone. To make the scene even more visceral, could you have him get more specific about the physical differences or the \"nature\" of these people? For example, how he might view their lack of technology or their \"savage\" appearance as proof that they are fundamentally different from the civilized man? Just something to really drive home his sense of superiority in the monologue.",
